---
title: Chicken Korma Curry & Butter Rice with Mango Chutney, Garlic Flatbreads & Mint Yoghurt
description: There's nothing like mildly-spiced curry made with creamy coconut milk for a warming weeknight meal. Make sure to use the flatbreads and butter-cashew rice to scoop up all that delicious goodness!
